Project based on learning uDemy course: https://jacintodesign.github.io/music-player/

Personalization and Improvements:
>Custom tracks (including one i produced, just for fun);
>Tracks data are stored into an external module (songList.js);
>Added playback controls with keyboard (space/enter and arrow keys);
>Automatic play when user select a point in the progress bar;
>Playback state maintains when skipping tracks;
>Event Delegation for track controls (to reduce the number of event handlers);
>Matching strategy to avoid click on unwanted area of the progress-container;
>Fix and improvements of responsive design;
>Small performances and UI tweak;
